    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing though. you can't find something that's gone. the person who could feel things, who had purpose... they're just dead. it's not like i'm lost in the woods, i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. how do you fix something that isn't even there anymore?",
